<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[الحبَلة]</span>: أصل الكرْم.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فِعلة]</span>، بكسر الفاء<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
